==English==

===Verb===
'''[[get]] [[on]] (somebody's) [[nerves]]'''

#{{idiom}} to [[bother]], [[annoy]], [[infuriate]], or [[incense]]
#:''That noise is really '''getting on my nerves'''. Can you be any quieter?''

